  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients diagnosed as avascular necrosis of hip and undergoing total hip replacement
             arthroplasty

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  hematologic disease

          -  anticoagulant medication

          -  preoperative hemoglobin &lt; 10 g/dl

          -  renal disease

          -  pulmonary disease (pulmonary edema, effusion)

          -  cardiovascular disease (coronary heart disease, congestive heart failure)
      </textblock>
